fpTreeDataStructure

Class ConditionalTree

  • java.lang.Object
    • fpTreeDataStructure.ConditionalTree

  • public class ConditionalTree
extends java.lang.Object
    this tree stores paths that: conditioned on the existence of one item listed in 'white list' (with support greater than threshold) based on its parent conditional tree, one can create a conditional tree furthered conditioned on some item: e.g. if the parent is conditioned on item X, then a child can be created by further conditioned on Y, which means the child is conditioned on X,Y both appears
    Author:
    Ting
